{"tid":1510743,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"124年前 短暫建立嘅臺灣民主國","createTime":"2019-08-27T09:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T10:18:15.000Z","uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb5c73333d0bd37965a317e464c8f7e20e51172","tid":1510743,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:53:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">臺灣民主國</span>是1895年短暫存在於臺灣的共和制政權，亦稱為<span style=\"color: red;\">福爾摩沙共和國（Republic of Formosa）</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCXd0Fi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCXd0Fi.jpg&h=ee10a50c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PdKLRMZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPdKLRMZ.jpg&h=77860a70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ta8Auyw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTa8Auyw.jpg&h=576ad68b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3tqCHTx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3tqCHTx.jpg&h=d567acdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大清在甲午戰爭戰敗後，被迫於該年4月簽訂《馬關條約》將臺灣、澎湖與周邊島嶼割讓予日本，遭到臺灣住民強烈反對，臺灣部分仕紳因而鼓動前清臺灣巡撫唐景崧在該年5月25日宣布建國，並由唐景崧擔任首任大總統。然而在隨後因日方接收臺灣而起的乙未戰爭中，其中部分民兵首先叛變，臺北遭到佔領，唐景崧不久後便逃亡廈門，第一共和迅速瓦解。該年6月26日，劉永福被選出任第二任大總統，以臺南為基地建立第二共和，並以大天后宮為總統府。但劉永福亦於該年10月19日西渡中國大陸，兩日後臺南遭日軍攻陷，臺灣民主國滅亡，歷時僅150天。儘管台日軍隊有數場激戰，日軍傷亡以病死者多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2AzjWdz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2AzjWdz.png&h=19511319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臺灣民主國是臺灣住民為了引起國際社會牽制日本統治而建立的，由年號定為「永清」便可看出其本質上奉清朝為宗主，並於獨立時闡明事成後（驅逐日本人）將回歸清朝統治。臺灣民主國的合法性並沒有得到任何國家承認，另有一種說法是：清廷起初默許，但在被德國警告假如開戰將賠償更多後，也不支持臺灣民主國，並要求唐景崧離臺赴京。"},{"pid":"f6260ada501d99d6672dee8bd10b5fc0585ca34a","tid":1510743,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e16b11dfa701d5b28564f6e1e6ce379bcd707478","tid":1510743,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:53:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j0K0rjRaD_g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dj0K0rjRaD_g&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=03cb349d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j0K0rjRaD_g</a>"},{"pid":"c89110a5611bc0ff952cd184ef79f725c48bf4f7","tid":1510743,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=5d1238a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=34126d0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=c31280cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"4ddaf18d70a94fba08473f3f80db8cc9761131ca","tid":1510743,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UH5RQh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UH5RQh.jpg&h=47f5